overview: On July 24th Homecoming, Part 1 is live on FITE! The event features three title matches and the first time ever match where 2 Cold Scorpio faces Grim Reefer. Check the full lineup below:  GCW Tag Team Championship Match  G-Raver and Jimmy Lloyd vs Second Gear Crew (Matthew Justice and Mance Warner)  Scramble Match  Dante Leon vs Atticus Cogar vs Jack Cartwheel vs Brayden Lee vs Jordan Oliver vs Shane Mercer  AJ Gray vs Nolan Edward  Tony Deppen vs Ninja Mack  Marko Stunt vs Starboy Charlie  2 Cold Scorpio vs Grim Reefer  GCW Ultraviolent Championship Match  Alex Colon vs Drew Parker  GCW World Championship Match  Nick Gage vs Matt Cardona
title: GCW Homecoming Part I
